MockTwitter
===========

MockTwitter generates JSON user defined responses. More is on the way.


Example
=======

On the way. They'll most likely be extracted from the RSpec tests.


In the works
=======

http://twitter.com/statuses/public_timeline.json
http://twitter.com/statuses/followers.json
http://twitter.com/statuses/friends.json


Completed
=======

http://twitter.com/statuses/user_timeline.json
http://twitter.com/statuses/show/#{id}.json
http://twitter.com/users/show/#{id}.json

Great tool for making JSON readable: http://jsonformatter.curiousconcept.com/


